    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine 2017 BMW M2, a definitive driver's machine preserved in showroom condition. Powered by the N55B30T0 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-six, it delivers linear power through a 6-speed manual gearbox and a computer-actuated Active M Differential. The chassis features lightweight forged aluminum control arms and a high-performance braking system with four-piston fixed calipers and cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously serviced, this F87 chassis exhibits zero mechanical wear and retains its factory-fresh structural integrity. For the discerning enthusiast, this example offers a pure, unmodified analog experience with the reliability of a modern classic.",
      "price": 48500.0,
